g.text: Acquisition of resources from the market
The instance representing the player in the model
contains an attribute that holds the resources obtained by the market.
The client will display this field, choose which resources to save
in the stock and ask the controller to save them.
If it is possible, the client receives ack message and the game continues.
Otherwise, he receives nack message and he will have to make the choice again.
In order not to increase the diagram further, it was decided not to represent
the case in which there is not enough space to save the selected resources.
Also, the view update messages have been omitted.
